==Somali==
* From the [[Arabic]] '''{{Unicode|&#1587;&#1615;&#1608;&#1602;}}''', [[Somali]] '''{{Unicode|sūqqa}}''' or '''{{Unicode|sūūq}}''' {{f}} meaning a big [[market]]. '''{{Unicode|sūūq}}''' means a market, it should not be confused with the [[term]] [[shop]] because in [[Somali]], the word [[shop]] is '''{{Unicode|dūkkāan}}'''.